Beat pudding mix and milk in medium bowl with whisk 2 min. Add cookie crumbs; mix well. Shape into 42 (1-inch) balls. Freeze 10 min. Dip in semi-sweet chocolate; place in single layer in shallow waxed paper-lined pan. Refrigerate 20 min. or until firm. Drizzle with white chocolate; refrigerate 10 min. or until firm.